SnapshotIndexShardStatus that = (SnapshotIndexShardStatus) o.     if (stage != that.stage)         return false.     if (stats != null ? !stats.equals(that.stats) : that.stats != null)         return false.     if (nodeId != null ? !nodeId.equals(that.nodeId) : that.nodeId != null)         return false.     return failure != null ? failure.equals(that.failure) : that.failure == null. }
